⚡ Pulse — Discord Utility Bot

Pulse is a modern, all-in-one Discord bot built to manage everything in your server with speed, simplicity, and style.

⚡ Managing everything here

✨ Features
🛠️ Utility
/ping — Check bot latency
/hello — Quick greeting
/uptime — See how long Pulse has been online
/botinfo — Info about Pulse
/avatar — Get a user's avatar
/userinfo — View user details
/serverinfo — Server statistics
/membercount — Member breakdown
🎉 Fun
/8ball — Ask a question
/coinflip — Flip a coin
/choose — Pick between options
/rate — Rate anything
/roll — Roll a dice
/meme — Fetch a random meme
/roast — Roast someone 💀
🛡️ Moderation (Full Pulse Access only)
/purge — Delete messages
/lock — Lock a channel
/unlock — Unlock a channel
/unlockall — Unlock all channels
/warn — Warn a user
/warnings — View warnings
/clearwarnings — Clear warnings
/nickname — Change nicknames
/slowmode — Set slowmode
🎟️ Ticket System
Create tickets via panel
Staff-only claim system
Add/remove users
Rename tickets
Close tickets with transcript logging
💡 Community
/suggest — Submit suggestions with voting
/remind — Set reminders
